{"tid":1326603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣片] 一齊走下去 721見","createTime":"2019-07-17T09:39:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T09:42:27.000Z","uid":169855,"like":78,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"06aa03c267e7a58db2ccc327c0c565218758985d","tid":1326603,"uid":169855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:39:59.000Z","msg":"整咗條片 提下大家點解721要上街<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JNBf5vX8o_w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJNBf5vX8o_w&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5aub3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=b19ef9a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JNBf5vX8o_w</a><br />\n<br />\n大家背負既係烈士們既遺願<br />\n721 大家代佢地一齊走下去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">一個都不能少<br />\n不流血，不受傷，不被捕<br />\n不分化，不篤灰，不割蓆<br />\n<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"66beb2862114f235d4168f50df973c92cb6a2000","tid":1326603,"uid":181549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:40:58.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"16701ba508f9e846af13a5cc49188b8963dbea61","tid":1326603,"uid":68822,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:42:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kVURRBwauKE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkVURRBwauKE&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5aub3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=dd6fc841\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kVURRBwauKE</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/F8Nr2YF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF8Nr2YF.jpg&h=37b27c1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1326334/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1326334/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[反送中]【Hongkongers! Assemble! 】- 光復香港，沒有暴民，只有暴政<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n不割蓆 不篤灰 不分化 不捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n七大訴求<br />\n- 全面落實雙真普選<br />\n- 永久完全撤回逃犯條<br />\n- 釋放所有反送中被捕抗爭示威者<br />\n- 成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n- 撤回暴動定性<br />\n- 永不實行社會信用評分系統<br />\n- 收回多功能智慧監控燈柱<br />\n<br />\n<em>&lsquo;It's not about how much we lost, it's about how much we have left.&rsquo; <span style=\"font-size: medium;\">(Avengers: Endgame)</span></em><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">721! HONGKONGERS! ASSEMBLE!</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"5e277b790040cd2ec54fd061ac7bf0437d25c5b1","tid":1326603,"uid":256914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:42:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7f8ee3955e941e3f608e6b7393c4e7545970e66a","tid":1326603,"uid":27084,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:46:31.000Z","msg":"有洋蔥架頂你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好放棄呀 出黎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f3b45551349d514cd2b137766f5475955770e4","tid":1326603,"uid":169855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f8ee3955e941e3f608e6b7393c4e7545970e66a","tid":1326603,"uid":27084,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:46:31.000Z","msg":"有洋蔥架頂你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好放棄呀 出黎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:51:38.000Z","msg":"催淚彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c7648f8ce2a6eff24962c6b15a18b3461176c2","tid":1326603,"uid":169855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:52:48.000Z","msg":